description: [``botocore``] Added support for hsm type hsm2m.medium. Added supported for creating a cluster in FIPS or NON_FIPS mode.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for configuration of evaluation method for composite rules in Glue Data Quality rulesets.
[``botocore``] Add RoamingDeviceSNR and RoamingDeviceRSSI to Customer Metrics.

[``botocore``] This feature allows customers to use their keys stored in KMS to derive a shared secret which can then be used to establish a secured channel for communication, provide proof of possession, or establish trust with other parties.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for CMAF ingest (DASH-IF live media ingest protocol interface 1)
